I received a yellow ribbon for guarding the Pope once, I don't think the Corps will allow me to wear it on my uniform. Not that I can fit into my uniform, besides the ex-wife kept them. Maybe she thought she could sell them or something. Probably never saw the bullet holes in them.<br><br>
Oh! and then I got one for the Ronnie King riots. No lie honest to goodness ribbon. dark blue and Grey in color with a 92' in the center. I never went back to pick mine up. Didn't want to be seen like a chest beater wearing all those ribbons &lt;G&gt;.<br><br>
